CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper April 19, 1958, pg. B3, reads: "Boys Club Week Speakers - This year's celebration of Boys Club Week, at Kay Boys Club, was highlighted on April 11 with an address by Dr. Harris W. Roberts (center), head of the sociology department, Virginia State College. He was introduced by Common Pleas Court Judge Homer S. Brown (right). The Rev. George D. Little (left), pastor of Friendship Community church, presided. The celebration closed on April 13, the 27th anniversary of Kay Boys Club. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Rev. George D. Little, Dr. Harry W. Roberts, and Homer S. Brown posed in Kay Boys Club during National Boy's Week program
